- cs.SD (Sound) is also a likely category as the paper deals with speech recognition systems.
- cs.LG (Machine Learning) is another likely category as the paper proposes a new approach to create an unit set for CTC based speech recognition systems.
- cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) is a possible category as the paper proposes a new approach for speech recognition systems using machine learning techniques.
- cs.SI (Speech and Audio Processing) is another possible category as the paper deals with speech recognition systems.
